Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:05.69,Italics_top,Narrator,0,0,0,,{The fact that there are those after Main \Nand her strong mana has come to light.}Những kẻ thèm muốn sức mạnh Ma lực của Myne đã lộ mặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:10.22,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Main's mana is unbelievably great.}Ma lực của con bé vô cùng khủng khiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:14.77,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{But if she can't control it, she is a \Ndanger to herself and those around her.}Nhưng nếu không thể kiểm soát được, con bé sẽ gây\N nguy hiểm cho bản thân và người xung quanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:19.27,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{If she is deemed dangerous,\N Main will be dealt with.}Nếu tôi thấy nguy hiểm, con bé sẽ bị xử lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.00,Italics_top,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Meanwhile, a blue-robed priest \Nshe had never seen before}Khi đó, một linh mục áo xanh Myne chưa từng gặp xuất hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:25.57,Italics_top,Narrator,0,0,0,,{appeared before her as she gets ready \Nto head to the Spring Prayer.}Ngay lúc cô bé chuẩn bị cho lễ Cầu Xuân.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:29.97,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Squeak "pwee" for me.}Kêu ụt ịt xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.87,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Well? Go on! Squeak.}Nào nào, kêu đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.37,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Go on, go on.}Nào nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:39.13,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,Cậu ta tính cách hơi có vấn đề.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.90,Default,Ferdinand,0,0,0,,{Just go ahead and humor him.}Làm theo ý hắn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.84,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Pwee!}Ụt ịt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:45.88,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Excellent.}Tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.63,Default,Sylvester,0,0,0,,{Now, keep squeaking!}Giờ thì kêu thêm đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.02,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Pwee! Pwee! Pwee...}Ụt ịt! Ụt ịt...
